measurements.description: Two hundred ninety round flowers and 156 buds on 29 up to 25.5-cm inflorescences; born on a 48-cm wide by 21-cm tall plant in a 20-cm plastic pot, grown in fir bark and coir; sepals and petals widely elliptic, peach overlaid rose, dark rose proximally; lip saccate, cream, light orange distally, side lobes dark rose; column white overlaid orange, anther cap light yellow; substance firm; texture crystalline.
